            "content_html": "<img src=\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/6077574?u=486e2475c94d11d34440e595364385949742c595&v=4\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\" alt=\"\"/><br/><h6 dir=\"auto\">Description of changes</h6>\n<p dir=\"auto\">Add a <code class=\"notranslate\">security.loginDefs.settings</code> option for the login.defs file to provide enhanced configuration abilities.</p>\n<p dir=\"auto\">E.g. add hardening options to login.defs file</p>\n<div class=\"snippet-clipboard-content notranslate position-relative overflow-auto\" data-snippet-clipboard-copy-content=\"security.loginDefs.settings.ENCRYPT_METHOD = &quot;SHA512&quot;;\nsecurity.loginDefs.settings.SHA_CRYPT_MIN_ROUNDS = 999999999;\nsecurity.loginDefs.settings.SHA_CRYPT_MAX_ROUNDS =  999999999;\nsecurity.loginDefs.settings.PASS_MAX_DAYS = 365;\nsecurity.loginDefs.settings.PASS_MIN_DAYS = 1;\"><pre class=\"notranslate\"><code class=\"notranslate\">security.loginDefs.settings.ENCRYPT_METHOD = \"SHA512\";\nsecurity.loginDefs.settings.SHA_CRYPT_MIN_ROUNDS = 999999999;\nsecurity.loginDefs.settings.SHA_CRYPT_MAX_ROUNDS =  999999999;\nsecurity.loginDefs.settings.PASS_MAX_DAYS = 365;\nsecurity.loginDefs.settings.PASS_MIN_DAYS = 1;\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<h6 dir=\"auto\">Things done</h6>\n\n<ul class=\"contains-task-list\">\n<li>Built on platform(s)\n<ul class=\"contains-task-list\">\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"\" disabled=\"\" class=\"task-list-item-checkbox\" checked=\"\"> x86_64-linux</li>\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"\" disabled=\"\" class=\"task-list-item-checkbox\"> aarch64-linux</li>\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"\" disabled=\"\" class=\"task-list-item-checkbox\"> x86_64-darwin</li>\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"\" disabled=\"\" class=\"task-list-item-checkbox\"> aarch64-darwin</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"\" disabled=\"\" class=